title: [Gyldemar Forest, Rocky Trail]
description: Sand and gravel continue to form the trail while oaks  form a wall of wood along the path.  A lone oak leans awkwardly, most of its trunk blackened.
Sand and gravel continue to form the trail while oaks form a wall of wood along the path.  A lone oak leans awkwardly in the star-filled sky, most of its trunk blackened.
